  01 Apr 2014; Christian Birchinger <joker@gentoo.org> +razercfg-0.24.ebuild:
  Version bump. Systemd unit file path fixed.

  23 Feb 2014; Christian Birchinger <joker@gentoo.org> -razercfg-0.22.ebuild:
  Remove old version

*razercfg-0.23 (23 Feb 2014)

  23 Feb 2014; Christian Birchinger <joker@gentoo.org> +razercfg-0.23.ebuild:
